text: Myrt may refer to: * World War II Allied reporting name of the Japanese Nakajima C6N reconnaissance aircraft * Myrtle "Myrt" Spear, a title character of the American radio show Myrt and Marge (1931–1942) and a 1933 film based on it * Myrt Basing (1900–1957), American National Football League player
title: Myrt
